oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print Poster Show and Sale
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Sherraden, Jim; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and brown on split fountain, blue to tan) announcing a Poster Show and Sale with Jim Sherraden at the Palace of the Governors on September 20 and the Museum of International Folk Art on October 1 and 2. Poster features woodcuts of a horse and rider and the Hatch Show Print logo.
